While we have always put our values of Respect, Integrity, Communication and
Excellence at the center of our company, today marks a renewal of our
commitment to those values, and to one value in particular, Communication.

Your feedback in the last Excellence Through Communication survey indicated
that we could do better job of communicating. With several initiatives
underway, we,ve been working hard to improve communication at Enron.

Please access IP-TV to hear a special message from Ken Lay about our
initiatives and our commitment to improving communication.  To view the
message, you must have IP-TV and a sound card installed on your computer.

